name: Globe Metal
overview:
Established in the year 1984, we, “Globe Metal Industries”, are a renowned firm engaged in manufacturing and supplying high grade Canteen Equipment, Hospital Furniture, Domestic Furniture and Office Furniture.

Our Products : In addition to these we offer, Plastic Disposable Product, Industrial Cooler, Sheet Metal Component, Ice Cream Packaging and Canteen Trolley.

Our Team: We are blessed with a team of highly skilled professionals who work in sync with one another to carry out all our business activities with ease. All our appointed professionals are highly qualified and hold immense expertise in their respective fields.

Our Infrastructure: We have established a modernized infrastructure facility for our firm, to have a trouble-free execution of all our business activities.

Why Us?: Clients can trust us for the following reasons:

High Quality Testing
Delivery On Time
Robust Infrastructure
Ethical Business Policy
